{"tid":1028058,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本 PlayStation Vita 主機將於近日停止供貨 宣告 PlayStation 掌上型主機業務的終結","createTime":"2019-02-19T08:37:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-19T09:36:38.000Z","uid":85180,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1e0c82810b05d1aaf9328c66260dedbbbc99e7d4","tid":1028058,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T08:37:02.000Z","msg":"日本 PlayStation Vita 主機將於近日停止供貨 宣告 PlayStation 掌上型主機業務的終結<br />\n（GNN 記者 Sam 報導） 2019-02-19 12:16:37<br />\n根據 PlayStation 日本官方網站的產品頁面訊息，目前僅有 2 款仍在販售中的 PlayStation Vita 掌上型主機「PlayStation Vita Wi-Fi 型號 黑」與「PlayStation Vita Wi-Fi 型號 水波藍」將於近日停止供貨，且目前並無後繼款式的消息，表示推出至今 7 年多的這款掌上型主機將走入歷史。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/25/1e55f606c3c4f75c81d894597d140j15.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F25%2F1e55f606c3c4f75c81d894597d140j15.JPG&h=9c188f68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nPlayStation Vita 是索尼互動娛樂於 2011 年 1 月發表的旗下第 2 代掌上型主機，承襲前代 PlayStation Portable 的造型設計與理念，以高效能整合處理器與細緻的 OLED 顯示螢幕提供當時最高等級的 3D 繪圖影音效果，並導入家用主機主流的雙類比搖桿以及獨特的雙面觸碰輸入。<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/14/0000467214.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F14%2F0000467214.JPG&h=888f567e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2011 年 1 月時任索尼電腦娛樂（SCE，後更名為索尼互動娛樂 SIE）總裁兼執行長的平井一夫正式發表代號「NGP」的 PSP 後繼機種，後定名為「PlayStation Vita」<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/84/0000543884.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F84%2F0000543884.JPG&h=4ac6a980&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2011 年推出的 PCH-1000 系列 PS Vita，採用鮮豔高對比的 OLED 顯示螢幕<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/B/2KU/66/0000865766.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FB%2F2KU%2F66%2F0000865766.JPG&h=922e014c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nPS Vita 於 2011 年底起陸續在日本、亞洲與歐美地區推出，雖然具備硬體優勢，但競爭產品 Nintendo 3DS 搶先於當年 3 月推出，且 8 月就閃電降價 1 萬日圓提振買氣。加上 9 月又宣布原本左右 PSP 買氣的《魔物獵人》系列新作將移籍到 N3DS 上推出，使得 PS Vita 未能繼承 PSP 的市場版圖。雖然後續在 SIE 主導下推出了多款性質類似的 &ldquo;共鬥&rdquo; 遊戲，但皆未能扭轉局勢。"},{"pid":"b22637d9b25af8fb27f6699bd9d5bda4d666cbd0","tid":1028058,"uid":49588,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T09:04:14.000Z","msg":"生不逢時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c565120e7e0780f5b7096108e8fcc1d88a598e9","tid":1028058,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T09:13:16.000Z","msg":"PSPGO變左黑歷史?"},{"pid":"3e2b76d84a1d243ed099800ab98c4329b27ea6e5","tid":1028058,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T09:17:46.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n出sony xperia play station phone即掂番啦"},{"pid":"fba74ffac5315230c28139394578958eff8d9410","tid":1028058,"uid":95520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T09:24:01.000Z","msg":"psp嘅年代做學生好幸福"},{"pid":"3788ca1f58f80e10be42ca26ea82a4031fa27896","tid":1028058,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T09:27:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f5b70cc7027cbf2bdb4e1a32a85aee0bdef35d29","tid":1028058,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T09:36:38.000Z","msg":"屌!到佢停產個日都無一個像樣的PSV模擬器，3DS都有個citra打下飛機呀!"}]}